# Test data files — these can be large or proprietary
*.stdf
*.std
*.atdf
*.atd
/testdata

# …but the curated samples published on the docs site must be committed
# (the *.stdf / *.atdf globs above match by extension regardless of directory,
#  so re-include the sample paths explicitly)
!/docs/samples/*.stdf
!/docs/samples/*.atdf

# Rust parser tests (packages/parsers) read fixtures from /sample_data — these
# must be committed or `npm run test:rust` fails on a clean CI checkout.
!/sample_data/*.stdf
!/sample_data/*.atdf
